==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fornicator
<hw>For"ni*ca`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>fornicateur</ets>, OF. <ets>fornicator</ets>, from L.
<ets>fornicator</ets>.]</ety> <def>An unmarried person, male or female,
who has criminal intercourse with the other sex; one guilty of
fornication.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fornicatress</ent>⟦br⟧
